{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2749640/extras/ViajeSteam.gif?t=1726252072\" /><br>Embark on a charming journey with Weefager, a small, round, pink creature who masters the power of ether. This mysterious element extracts the souls of enemies and brings them back to life, transforming them into objects found throughout the world. In their new forms, they join your adventure, following your path. Overcome challenges and uncover secrets in a wondrous world. Lead your loyal spirits, exploring their unique abilities and the surrounding landscape, accompanied by an unforgettable soundtrack and a charismatic protagonist.<br><br>Weefager is a 2D platformer metroidvania, with its magic lying in innovative gameplay mechanics centered around soul collection and their functionalities once transformed into living objects.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2749640/extras/LanzaSteam.gif?t=1726252072\" /><br><br>Imagine turning a rock into a powerful gunslinger to defend you from dangers. All opportunities and combinations open up with the power of ether.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2749640/extras/AlmaSteam.gif?t=1726252072\" /><br><br>This pink ball isn't as innocent and cute as it seems; the game also delves into the complex human themes surrounding life, death, and existence.<br><br>Plan different strategies to overcome obstacles and advance in the world, facing mysterious characters and diving into the depths of Weefager's planet, discovering its hidden stories and secrets.<br><br>Meet some of the enemies and discover their abilities:<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2749640/extras/PuffySteam.gif?t=1726252072\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_